{"tid":1750972,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"正式宣佈今晚將會係「階段性勝利」！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-11-24T14:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T16:53:00.000Z","uid":37688,"like":560,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"3337ddf067f6161c1934b474845d4c832f500470","tid":1750972,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">階段性勝你老母</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論今晚結果係點，<br />\n依個區選只係好細既支線任，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要多謝勇武無同和理非割蓆比我地投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n投票之後仲有好長既路要行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁多個月被捕被打被姦既手足唔係condom!!!</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n無本土投而含淚投既人亦都<br />\n唔該好好監察住你地自己投出黎既議員！！<br />\n<br />\n繼續<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"bcd8ed00cc1cab44ce504e5f1796b6f51f3a43ea","tid":1750972,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7e2d858310097f3901fc6c0f3d45d4eb5141006","tid":1750972,"uid":37688,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"未贏咖"},{"pid":"175b5ece785923bb3a2551d46b2487821d87256b","tid":1750972,"uid":2607,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime